{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":25,"text":"So a few weeks ago, a friend"},{"time":2722,"text":"of mine gave this toy car to his"},{"time":4976,"text":"8-year-old son."},{"time":6587,"text":"But instead of going into a store and buying one,"},{"time":9408,"text":"like we do normally, he went to this"},{"time":12203,"text":"website and he downloaded"},{"time":14118,"text":"a file, and then he printed it"},{"time":16287,"text":"on this printer."},{"time":18142,"text":"So this idea that you can"},{"time":20121,"text":"manufacture objects"},{"time":22068,"text":"digitally using these machines"},{"time":23631,"text":"is something that The Economist magazine"},{"time":25309,"text":"defined as the Third Industrial Revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27939,"text":"Actually, I argue that there is another revolution"},{"time":31782,"text":"going on, and it's the one that has to do with"},{"time":34380,"text":"open-source hardware and the maker's movement,"},{"time":36908,"text":"because the printer that my friend used"},{"time":40667,"text":"to print the toy is actually open-source."},{"time":43284,"text":"So you go to the same website, you can download all the files"},{"time":46777,"text":"that you need in order to make that printer:"},{"time":50534,"text":"the construction files, the hardware, the software,"},{"time":54046,"text":"all the instruction is there."},{"time":56855,"text":"And also this is part of a large"},{"time":58975,"text":"community where there are thousands of people"},{"time":61575,"text":"around the world that are actually"},{"time":63535,"text":"making these kinds of printers,"},{"time":65078,"text":"and there's a lot of innovation"},{"time":66550,"text":"happening because it's all open-source."},{"time":68464,"text":"You don't need anybody's permission to create something great."},{"time":72352,"text":"And that space is like"},{"time":74713,"text":"the personal computer in 1976,"},{"time":77509,"text":"like the Apples with the other companies are fighting,"},{"time":79867,"text":"and we will see in a few years,"},{"time":82248,"text":"there will be the Apple of this kind of market come out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85381,"text":"Well, there's also another interesting thing."},{"time":89184,"text":"I said the electronics are open-source, because at the heart"},{"time":91148,"text":"of this printer there is something I'm really attached to:"},{"time":94129,"text":"these Arduino boards, the motherboard that sort of"},{"time":97080,"text":"powers this printer, is a project"},{"time":99287,"text":"I've been working on for the past seven years."},{"time":101710,"text":"It's an open-source project."},{"time":103271,"text":"I worked with these friends of mine that I have here."},{"time":106292,"text":"So the five of us, two Americans, two Italians"},{"time":108946,"text":"and a Spaniard, we — (Laughter)"},{"time":111927,"text":"You know, it's a worldwide project. (Laughter)"},{"time":115002,"text":"So we came together in this"},{"time":116871,"text":"design institute called the Interaction Design Institute"},{"time":119494,"text":"Ivrea, which was teaching"},{"time":121643,"text":"interaction design, this idea that you can take"},{"time":123941,"text":"design from the simple shape"},{"time":126492,"text":"of an object and you can move it"},{"time":128269,"text":"forward to design the way you interact with things."},{"time":130321,"text":"Well, when you design an object that's supposed to interact"},{"time":133213,"text":"with a human being, if you make a foam model"},{"time":135021,"text":"of a mobile phone, it doesn't make any sense."},{"time":137844,"text":"You have to have something that"},{"time":139350,"text":"actually interacts with people."},{"time":141857,"text":"So, we worked on Arduino and"},{"time":144976,"text":"a lot of other projects there to"},{"time":146792,"text":"create platforms that would be"},{"time":148693,"text":"simple for our students to use,"},{"time":150877,"text":"so that our students could just build things that worked,"},{"time":153338,"text":"but they don't have five years to become an electronics engineer. We have one month."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157396,"text":"So how do I make something that even a kid can use?"},{"time":160051,"text":"And actually, with Arduino,"},{"time":162952,"text":"we have kids like Sylvia that you see here,"},{"time":165375,"text":"that actually make projects with Arduino."},{"time":167247,"text":"I have 11-year-old kids stop me and show me"},{"time":169855,"text":"stuff they built for Arduino that's really"},{"time":172674,"text":"scary to see the capabilities"},{"time":174415,"text":"that kids have when you give them the tools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176838,"text":"So let's look at what happens when you make a tool"},{"time":179818,"text":"that anybody can just pick up and build something quickly,"},{"time":182665,"text":"so one of the examples that I like to sort of"},{"time":184533,"text":"kick off this discussion is this"},{"time":186447,"text":"example of this cat feeder."},{"time":188177,"text":"The gentleman who made this project had two cats."},{"time":190744,"text":"One was sick and the other one"},{"time":192478,"text":"was healthy, so he had to make"},{"time":194856,"text":"sure they ate the proper food."},{"time":196544,"text":"So he made this thing that recognizes the cat"},{"time":198703,"text":"from a chip mounted inside"},{"time":200840,"text":"on the collar of the cat, and opens the door"},{"time":203560,"text":"and the cat can eat the food."},{"time":205304,"text":"This is made by recycling an old CD player"},{"time":207094,"text":"that you can get from an old computer,"},{"time":209307,"text":"some cardboard, tape, couple of sensors, a few blinking LEDs,"},{"time":212763,"text":"and then suddenly you have a tool. You build something"},{"time":215551,"text":"that you cannot find on the market."},{"time":217488,"text":"And I like this phrase: \"Scratch your own itch.\""},{"time":220252,"text":"If you have an idea, you just go and you make it."},{"time":222847,"text":"This is the equivalent of sketching on paper"},{"time":224796,"text":"done with electronics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227368,"text":"So one of the features that I"},{"time":229116,"text":"think is important about our work"},{"time":230944,"text":"is that our hardware, on top of"},{"time":233716,"text":"being made with love in Italy —"},{"time":235906,"text":"as you can see from the"},{"time":237659,"text":"back of the circuit — (Laughter)"},{"time":239688,"text":"is that it's open,"},{"time":241528,"text":"so we publish all the design"},{"time":243496,"text":"files for the circuit online,"},{"time":245224,"text":"so you can download it and"},{"time":247207,"text":"you can actually use it to"},{"time":249047,"text":"make something, or to modify, to learn."},{"time":251680,"text":"You know, when I was learning about programming,"},{"time":252949,"text":"I learned by looking at other people's code,"},{"time":254826,"text":"or looking at other people's circuits in magazines."},{"time":258255,"text":"And this is a good way to learn,"},{"time":260471,"text":"by looking at other people's work."},{"time":262712,"text":"So the different elements of the project are all open,"},{"time":265304,"text":"so the hardware is released"},{"time":267007,"text":"with a Creative Commons license."},{"time":269071,"text":"So, you know, I like this idea that hardware becomes"},{"time":271097,"text":"like a piece of culture that you share"},{"time":273236,"text":"and you build upon, like it was"},{"time":275195,"text":"a song or a poem with Creative Commons."},{"time":278832,"text":"Or, the software is GPL, so it's open-source as well."},{"time":281508,"text":"The documentation and the hands-on teaching"},{"time":284935,"text":"methodology is also open-source and released as the Creative Commons."},{"time":288518,"text":"Just the name is protected so"},{"time":290521,"text":"that we can make sure that we can tell people"},{"time":293267,"text":"what is Arduino and what isn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295907,"text":"Now, Arduino itself is made of"},{"time":297579,"text":"a lot of different open-source components"},{"time":299819,"text":"that maybe individually are hard to use for"},{"time":302570,"text":"a 12-year-old kid, so Arduino"},{"time":304677,"text":"wraps everything together into"},{"time":306530,"text":"a mashup of open-source technologies"},{"time":308796,"text":"where we try to give them the"},{"time":310668,"text":"best user experience to get something done quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312875,"text":"So you have situations like this,"},{"time":315746,"text":"where some people in Chile"},{"time":317684,"text":"decided to make their own boards instead of buying them,"},{"time":320482,"text":"to organize a workshop and"},{"time":322407,"text":"to save money. Or there are"},{"time":325507,"text":"companies that make their own"},{"time":327452,"text":"variations of Arduino that fit"},{"time":329221,"text":"in a certain market, and there's"},{"time":330972,"text":"probably, maybe like a 150 of them"},{"time":333685,"text":"or something at the moment."},{"time":335477,"text":"This one is made by a company"},{"time":337365,"text":"called Adafruit, which is run by"},{"time":339309,"text":"this woman called Limor Fried,"},{"time":341621,"text":"also known as Ladyada, who is"},{"time":343228,"text":"one of the heroes of the open-source hardware movement"},{"time":345949,"text":"and the maker movement."},{"time":347483,"text":"So, this idea that you have a new, sort of"},{"time":350437,"text":"turbo-charged DIY community"},{"time":353221,"text":"that believes in open-source,"},{"time":354901,"text":"in collaboration, collaborates"},{"time":357101,"text":"online, collaborates in different spaces."},{"time":359542,"text":"There is this magazine called Make that sort of gathered"},{"time":362664,"text":"all these people and sort of put them together"},{"time":364204,"text":"as a community, and you see"},{"time":366636,"text":"a very technical project explained in a"},{"time":368664,"text":"very simple language, beautifully typeset."},{"time":371521,"text":"Or you have websites,"},{"time":373089,"text":"like this one, like Instructables,"},{"time":375350,"text":"where people actually teach each other about anything."},{"time":377354,"text":"So this one is about Arduino projects,"},{"time":379099,"text":"the page you see on the screen, but effectively here you can"},{"time":382660,"text":"learn how to make a cake and everything else."},{"time":385238,"text":"So let's look at some projects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388038,"text":"So this one is a quadcopter."},{"time":389654,"text":"It's a small model helicopter."},{"time":391369,"text":"In a way, it's a toy, no?"},{"time":393639,"text":"And so this one was military technology"},{"time":395932,"text":"a few years ago, and now it's"},{"time":397853,"text":"open-source, easy to use, you can buy it online."},{"time":400495,"text":"DIY Drones is the community; they do this thing called ArduCopter."},{"time":404413,"text":"But then somebody actually launched this start-up called"},{"time":407426,"text":"Matternet, where they figured out that you could"},{"time":409619,"text":"use this to actually transport"},{"time":411917,"text":"things from one village to another in Africa,"},{"time":414350,"text":"and the fact that this was easy to find,"},{"time":415918,"text":"open-source, easy to hack, enabled them"},{"time":418530,"text":"to prototype their company really quickly."},{"time":420668,"text":"Or, other projects. Matt Richardson: I'm getting a little sick"},{"time":423357,"text":"of hearing about the same people on TV over and over and over"},{"time":426613,"text":"again, so I decided to do something about it."},{"time":429823,"text":"This Arduino project,"},{"time":431237,"text":"which I call the Enough Already, will mute the TV anytime"},{"time":434612,"text":"any of these over-exposed"},{"time":436587,"text":"personalities is mentioned. (Laughter)"},{"time":437819,"text":"I'll show you how I made it. (Applause)"},{"time":442667,"text":"MB: Check this out."},{"time":444491,"text":"MR: Our producers caught up with Kim Kardashian earlier"},{"time":446448,"text":"today to find out what she was planning on wearing to her —"},{"time":449351,"text":"MB: Eh? (Laughter)"},{"time":450742,"text":"MR: It should do a pretty good"},{"time":452644,"text":"job of protecting our ears from having to hear about the details"},{"time":454311,"text":"of Kim Kardashian's wedding."},{"time":456107,"text":"MB: Okay. So, you know, again, what is interesting here"},{"time":460664,"text":"is that Matt found this module"},{"time":463634,"text":"that lets Arduino process"},{"time":465866,"text":"TV signals, he found some code"},{"time":467755,"text":"written by somebody else that generates infrared signals for the TV,"},{"time":470584,"text":"put it together and then created this great project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472934,"text":"It's also used, Arduino's used,"},{"time":474986,"text":"in serious places like, you know, the Large Hadron Collider."},{"time":477886,"text":"There's some Arduino balls collecting data and sort of"},{"time":480595,"text":"measuring some parameters."},{"time":482395,"text":"Or it's used for —"},{"time":484714,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":495426,"text":"So this is a musical interface"},{"time":497867,"text":"built by a student from Italy,"},{"time":499986,"text":"and he's now turning this into"},{"time":502106,"text":"a product. Because it was a"},{"time":503964,"text":"student project becoming a product."},{"time":506195,"text":"Or it can be used to make an assistive device."},{"time":508139,"text":"This is a glove that understands"},{"time":510129,"text":"the sign language and transforms"},{"time":512276,"text":"the gestures you make into sounds"},{"time":514475,"text":"and writes the words that you're signing on a display"},{"time":517791,"text":"And again, this is made of all different parts you can find"},{"time":519137,"text":"on all the websites that sell Arduino-compatible parts,"},{"time":522086,"text":"and you assemble it into a project."},{"time":524170,"text":"Or this is a project from the ITP part of NYU,"},{"time":527491,"text":"where they met with this boy"},{"time":529218,"text":"who has a severe disability, cannot play with the PS3,"},{"time":532236,"text":"so they built this device that"},{"time":534179,"text":"allows the kid to play baseball"},{"time":536626,"text":"although he has limited"},{"time":538523,"text":"movement capability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540899,"text":"Or you can find it in arts projects."},{"time":543049,"text":"So this is the txtBomber."},{"time":545364,"text":"So you put a message into this device"},{"time":547001,"text":"and then you roll it on the wall, and it basically"},{"time":549844,"text":"has all these solenoids"},{"time":551746,"text":"pressing the buttons on spray cans,"},{"time":553538,"text":"so you just pull it over a wall"},{"time":555174,"text":"and it just writes on the wall"},{"time":556901,"text":"all the political messages."},{"time":559363,"text":"So, yeah. (Applause)"},{"time":561994,"text":"Then we have this plant here."},{"time":564034,"text":"This is called Botanicalls,"},{"time":565924,"text":"because there's an Arduino ball with a Wi-Fi module"},{"time":569119,"text":"in the plant, and it's measuring"},{"time":571720,"text":"the well-being of the plant,"},{"time":573235,"text":"and it's creating a Twitter account"},{"time":575225,"text":"where you can actually interact with the plant. (Laughter)"},{"time":578754,"text":"So, you know, this plant"},{"time":580684,"text":"will start to say, \"This is really hot,\" or"},{"time":583163,"text":"there's a lot of, you know, \"I need water right now.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":587234,"text":"So it just gives a personality to your plant."},{"time":590657,"text":"Or this is something that twitters when the"},{"time":593324,"text":"baby inside the belly of a"},{"time":595290,"text":"pregnant woman kicks. (Laughter)"},{"time":597898,"text":"Or this is a 14-year-old kid in"},{"time":599489,"text":"Chile who made a system that"},{"time":601609,"text":"detects earthquakes and publishes on Twitter."},{"time":603933,"text":"He has 280,000 followers."},{"time":606421,"text":"He's 14 and he anticipated"},{"time":608565,"text":"a governmental project by one year. (Applause)"},{"time":612204,"text":"Or again, another project where,"},{"time":615945,"text":"by analyzing the Twitter feed"},{"time":617691,"text":"of a family, you can basically"},{"time":619627,"text":"point where they are, like in the \"Harry Potter\" movie."},{"time":622369,"text":"So you can find out everything about this project on the website."},{"time":625185,"text":"Or somebody made a chair that twitters when somebody farts. (Laughter)"},{"time":629866,"text":"It's interesting how, in 2009,"},{"time":632949,"text":"Gizmodo basically defined,"},{"time":635331,"text":"said that this project actually gives a meaning to Twitter,"},{"time":638094,"text":"so it was — a lot changed in between. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":641355,"text":"So very serious project."},{"time":642799,"text":"When the Fukushima disaster happened,"},{"time":645006,"text":"a bunch of people in Japan, they realized that the information"},{"time":648008,"text":"that the government was giving wasn't really open"},{"time":650563,"text":"and really reliable, so they built"},{"time":652313,"text":"this Geiger counter, plus Arduino, plus network"},{"time":655089,"text":"interface. They made 100"},{"time":657021,"text":"of them and gave them to people around Japan, and essentially"},{"time":660599,"text":"the data that they gathered gets published on this website"},{"time":662859,"text":"called Cosm, another website"},{"time":665008,"text":"they built, so you can actually get reliable real-time"},{"time":668649,"text":"information from the field,"},{"time":670474,"text":"and you can get unbiased information."},{"time":674081,"text":"Or this machine here, it's from"},{"time":675964,"text":"the DIY bio movement,"},{"time":678404,"text":"and it's one of the steps that you need in order to process DNA,"},{"time":680728,"text":"and again, it's completely open-source from the ground up."},{"time":684106,"text":"Or you have students in developing countries making"},{"time":687500,"text":"replicas of scientific instruments that cost"},{"time":690489,"text":"a lot of money to make."},{"time":692400,"text":"Actually they just build them themselves for a lot less"},{"time":694990,"text":"using Arduino and a few parts."},{"time":696223,"text":"This is a pH probe."},{"time":698119,"text":"Or you get kids, like these kids, they're from Spain."},{"time":701517,"text":"They learned how to program and to make robots when they"},{"time":704381,"text":"were probably, like, 11, and then they started to use Arduino"},{"time":707050,"text":"to make these robots that play football. They became"},{"time":709043,"text":"world champions by making an Arduino-based robot."},{"time":711885,"text":"And so when we had to make"},{"time":713761,"text":"our own educational robot, we just went to them and said,"},{"time":716573,"text":"you know, \"You design it, because you know exactly"},{"time":718921,"text":"what is needed to make a great robot that excites kids.\""},{"time":722651,"text":"Not me. I'm an old guy."},{"time":724327,"text":"What am I supposed to excite, huh? (Laughter)"},{"time":726863,"text":"But as I — in terms of educational assets. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":730798,"text":"There's also companies like Google"},{"time":732696,"text":"that are using the technology"},{"time":734647,"text":"to create interfaces between"},{"time":737521,"text":"mobile phones, tablets and the real world."},{"time":740914,"text":"So the Accessory Development Kit"},{"time":741934,"text":"from Google is open-source"},{"time":743986,"text":"and based on Arduino, as opposed"},{"time":745368,"text":"to the one from Apple which is"},{"time":747025,"text":"closed-source, NDA, sign your"},{"time":749529,"text":"life to Apple. Here you are."},{"time":752094,"text":"There's a giant maze, and Joey's sitting there, and the"},{"time":754674,"text":"maze is moving when you tilt the tablet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758858,"text":"Also, I come from Italy, and the design is important"},{"time":761830,"text":"in Italy, and yet very conservative."},{"time":764177,"text":"So we worked with a design"},{"time":765594,"text":"studio called Habits, in Milan,"},{"time":767760,"text":"to make this mirror, which is completely open-source."},{"time":770448,"text":"This doubles also as an iPod speaker."},{"time":773633,"text":"So the idea is that the hardware, the software,"},{"time":777270,"text":"the design of the object, the fabrication,"},{"time":778738,"text":"everything about this project is open-source"},{"time":781223,"text":"and you can make it yourself."},{"time":783093,"text":"So we want other designers to pick this up and learn how"},{"time":785447,"text":"to make great devices, to learn"},{"time":788058,"text":"how to make interactive products"},{"time":789736,"text":"by starting from something real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792505,"text":"But when you have this idea,"},{"time":794906,"text":"you know, what happens to all these ideas?"},{"time":796819,"text":"There's, like, thousands of ideas that I —"},{"time":798697,"text":"You know, it would take seven hours for me to do"},{"time":800857,"text":"all the presentations."},{"time":802737,"text":"I will not take all the seven hours. Thank you."},{"time":805785,"text":"But let's start from this example:"},{"time":807801,"text":"So, the group of people"},{"time":809729,"text":"that started this company called Pebble, they prototyped"},{"time":812140,"text":"a watch that communicates via Bluetooth with your phone,"},{"time":815832,"text":"and you can display information"},{"time":817368,"text":"on it. And they prototyped with"},{"time":819640,"text":"an old LCD screen from a Nokia"},{"time":821585,"text":"mobile phone and an Arduino."},{"time":823993,"text":"And then, when they had a final"},{"time":825826,"text":"project, they actually went to Kickstarter"},{"time":828234,"text":"and they were asking for 100,000 dollars to make"},{"time":830853,"text":"a few of them to sell."},{"time":832708,"text":"They got 10 million dollars."},{"time":834779,"text":"They got a completely"},{"time":836314,"text":"fully funded start-up, and they don't have to,"},{"time":839027,"text":"you know, get VCs involved or anything,"},{"time":840879,"text":"just excite the people with their great project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843747,"text":"The last project I want to show you is this:"},{"time":846031,"text":"It's called ArduSat. It's currently on Kickstarter,"},{"time":849769,"text":"so if you want to contribute, please do it."},{"time":852076,"text":"It's a satellite that goes into space, which is probably"},{"time":854886,"text":"the least open-source thing you can imagine,"},{"time":856808,"text":"and it contains an Arduino"},{"time":858859,"text":"connected to a bunch of sensors. So if you know how to use Arduino,"},{"time":861969,"text":"you can actually upload your experiments"},{"time":864425,"text":"into this satellite and run them."},{"time":866616,"text":"So imagine, if you as a high school can have the satellite"},{"time":869252,"text":"for a week and do satellite"},{"time":871601,"text":"space experiments like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":874253,"text":"So, as I said, there's"},{"time":877009,"text":"lots of examples, and I'm going to stop here. And I just"},{"time":878568,"text":"want to thank the Arduino community"},{"time":881084,"text":"for being the best, and just"},{"time":882754,"text":"every day making lots of projects."},{"time":884946,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":888410,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":890737,"text":"And thanks to the community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893224,"text":"Chris Anderson: Massimo,"},{"time":895197,"text":"you told me earlier today that you had no idea, of course,"},{"time":897802,"text":"that it would take off like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":899274,"text":"MB: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900063,"text":"CA: I mean, how must you feel when you read this stuff and you"},{"time":901859,"text":"see what you've unlocked?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":904360,"text":"MB: Well, it's the work of a lot of people, so we as a community"},{"time":907179,"text":"are enabling people to make"},{"time":908973,"text":"great stuff, and I just feel overwhelmed."},{"time":911475,"text":"It's just, it's difficult to describe this."},{"time":913644,"text":"Every morning, I wake up and I look at all the stuff that"},{"time":915658,"text":"Google Alerts sends me, and it's"},{"time":917844,"text":"just amazing. It's just"},{"time":919379,"text":"going into every field that you can imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922052,"text":"CA: Thank you so much. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":924044,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}